WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
This is a comfy little chair and that is a really good book.

00:06.000 --> 00:11.000
Now sit down on your comfy little chair and crack open that book.

00:11.000 --> 00:15.000
Read up to 30 to 60 minutes without interruptions from

00:15.000 --> 00:19.000
your phone, from your friends, from your cat or dog.

00:20.000 --> 00:22.000
Do the same thing tomorrow

00:22.000 --> 00:25.000
and that is how you read more books!